<section class="section" id="about" aria-labelledby="about-heading">
	<div class="shell about-grid">
		<div><p class="eyebrow">01 — About</p><h2 class="display section-title" id="about-heading">A beginner’s mind is a superpower.</h2></div>
		<div class="about-copy"><p>I’m Harry, an Information Engineering student at the Chinese University of Hong Kong. I enjoy tracing an idea from its first spark to a working program — whether that’s a game system, a useful bot, or a closer look at how computers work.</p><p>Right now, I’m moving toward two long-term goals: making indie games and growing a deeper understanding of hardware.</p><div class="values" aria-label="Personal values"><article class="value glass-card"><span aria-hidden="true">✦</span><h3>Curiosity first</h3><p>I keep learning, asking better questions, and staying open to the next idea.</p></article><article class="value glass-card"><span aria-hidden="true">↗</span><h3>Adaptable by design</h3><p>I’m comfortable finding my footing in new tools, problems, and possibilities.</p></article></div></div>
	</div>
</section>

